com.revature.rideshare.matching.beans

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revature.rideshare.matching.beans.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class User. Used by UserClient, a FeignClient for accessing the User Service. Used in MatchService to match User rider to User driver.
